odule on the classpath resolves to a single, consistent\nversion. Without the BOM the netty-all uber jar mixes with older individual\nnetty modules pulled transitively (e.g. via Artemis and reactor-netty),\nwhich causes runtime errors such as AbstractMethodError and\nNoClassDefFoundError (e.g. io/netty/util/LeakPresenceDetector).\n\nThis mirrors the alignment already on the 2.41 and 2.42 branches and closes\nthe same gap on 2.43. It also unblocks the reactor-netty-http 1.3.5 upgrade\n(#23878), which references netty classes only present in newer 4.2.x.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"75385c7a79d77bbda401c2f7f037dd89f746cff2","tree_id":"f3b5cdfe0173c5f39d4f1fd00bb4ae799f7d9137","timestamp":"2026-05-31T10:22:16Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/repos","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/subscriptions"},"name":"dhis2-core","full_name":"dhi